{"tid":2439151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍：繼續保持軍費增長，絕不容忍「台獨」分裂勢力","createTime":"2021-03-09T04:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:55:50.000Z","uid":278587,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ececeabfe4f95189d805eddb851a624f5c58fc60","tid":2439151,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426640&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=86c31fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426640&h=952a87d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426640</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中國今年軍費預算近一萬四千億元人民幣，比去年增加6.8%。解放軍表示，中國會繼續保持軍費的適度穩定增長。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍東部戰區第73集團軍的裝甲分隊展開晝夜實彈射擊考核，軍團被視為是攻佔台灣的主力。在北京出席人大會議的解放軍和武警部隊代表團新聞發言人表示，民進黨當局頑固堅持「台獨」分裂立場，是台海和平穩定的最大現實威脅。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍和武警部隊代表團新聞發言人吳謙：「我們願以最大誠意、盡最大努力，爭取兩岸和平統一的前景，但絕不容忍『台獨』分裂勢力，分裂祖國。我們不承諾放棄使用武力，保留採取一切必要措施的選項。」<br />\n<br />\n吳謙又批評民進黨挾洋自重，妄圖「以武謀獨」，嚴重危害台海和平穩定是十分危險和沒有出路。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國今年的軍費增長6.8%，達到近一萬四千億元人民幣，吳謙解釋中國政府堅持國防建設和經濟建設，協調發展方針，合理確定國防支出規模。<br />\n<br />\n增加的軍費主要用於保障重大工程啟動實施、加速武器裝備升級換代、加快推進軍事訓練轉型，構建新型軍事人才培養體系以及改善官兵生活福利待遇。<br />\n<br />\n吳謙強調，強國必須強軍，軍強才能國安，目前國土安全面臨的風險挑戰不容易忽視，陸地邊界爭議尚未徹底解決，島嶼領土問題和海洋劃界爭端依然存在。"},{"pid":"de2877de61fcda5c951ea537183780818f13d0c7","tid":2439151,"uid":224533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"繼續掠水<br />\n2021年前武統全宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d829f24743e3b87aeb070db7d50351e2c0dfdd6e","tid":2439151,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"北洋艦隊都係咁玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e87f5dd8ac7a55f9b6d6255805d0712fa2ba38","tid":2439151,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"支持R多啲 俾啲軍官吃喝嫖賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd334dc1613441ac2ba9482bb15c4a2d0054668","tid":2439151,"uid":216810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3PHJrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3PHJrZ.jpg&h=41654f2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"939a8282fd26ad36e1a68f1fa485efb7eb80db5f","tid":2439151,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20191231141107715808.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20191231141107715808.JPG&h=4093e147&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d12a9a836788322704f2a482c57021b472f7750e","tid":2439151,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6v3ELFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6v3ELFP.jpg&h=a43b27bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5d297a15345108f927cff4c92a47ab7cefbf6e","tid":2439151,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"你地打啦"},{"pid":"3ec789d62fd206bee1e238efbcfbd164cd6da9ee","tid":2439151,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"翠種唔找數就解放北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}